OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThames Water boss quits    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter sewage spills        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The chief executive of Thames Water has
OL,6, stepped down after two years in the    
OL,7, role, weeks after giving up her bonus  
OL,8, over sewage spills.                    
OL,10,FThames Water said Sarah Bentley would  
OL,11,Fleave with immediate effect, but would 
OL,12,Fcontinue to support the firm until her 
OL,13,Freplacement was found.                 
OL,15,FLast month Ms Bentley said she would   
OL,16,Fforgo her bonus due to the company's   
OL,17,Fpoor performance.                      
OL,19,FRaw sewage discharges into rivers had  
OL,20,Fbecome a problem for the firm.         
